<p>Israeli airstrikes across Gaza on Saturday killed at least 20 people, with local officials reporting between 20 and 24 dead and dozens wounded, amid a fragile cease-fire in place since October 10 [nytimes.com#1][ndtv.com#1][al-monitor.com#1][bbc.com#1][pbs.org#1][france24.com#2]. Israel said the strikes followed gunfire by an “armed terrorist” who crossed the so‑called Yellow Line inside Gaza and fired at soldiers [bbc.com#1][al-monitor.com#1]. Hamas accused Israel of violating the truce and urged U.S. intervention, while Israeli officials said five senior Hamas members were killed in the strikes [ndtv.com#1][aljazeera.com#2][pbs.org#1][france24.com#2].</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/mUjBCbatp-QtQQbkB1ZTJ9cheNrjf_XJnfdjVf1X-2jepWDNsUN1fgN-9ElnedQ3CojVq2mmB9dqKpO998ARkG-UeP1ANgizYQMKoGOHbEPVKH5CiuOmRC3OicGi6snhCDc8zxVCJEQelI2cUnpgUJjmcCggq4iejaGmppJQRlld6U-LrzToCzuqVchANlV2JqHQ9A' alt='Rescue workers extinguish a fire after an airstrike in Gaza City.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Casualty figures ranged from 20 to 24 dead, with dozens wounded, according to Gaza medical and civil defense officials and hospitals [nytimes.com#1][ndtv.com#1][al-monitor.com#1][bbc.com#1][pbs.org#1][france24.com#2].</li><li>IDF rationale: The military said it struck after an “armed terrorist” crossed the Yellow Line—an internal demarcation behind which Israeli forces withdrew—and opened fire on troops [bbc.com#1][al-monitor.com#1].</li><li>Targeted leaders: Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu’s office said five senior Hamas members were killed in the strikes [pbs.org#1][france24.com#1][france24.com#2][timesofisrael.com#1].</li><li>Children among victims: Reports included four children killed in the Nuseirat refugee camp and children among the wounded in separate attacks [aljazeera.com#3][aljazeera.com#2][pbs.org#1].</li><li>Cease-fire context: The U.S.-brokered cease-fire began on October 10; violence has repeatedly flared since, killing hundreds of Palestinians and at least three Israeli soldiers [al-monitor.com#1][pbs.org#1][france24.com#2][nytimes.com#1].</li><li>Strike methods: Among the attacks, an Israeli “kamikaze” drone blew up a vehicle on a busy Gaza City street [aljazeera.com#1].</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Israeli military (IDF): Israel says the airstrikes were a response to an armed assailant crossing the Yellow Line and firing at soldiers [bbc.com#1][al-monitor.com#1] (<a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c20879zzqn8o'>BBC; Al-Monitor</a>)</li><li>Hamas: Hamas accuses Israel of violating the truce and calls on the United States to intervene [ndtv.com#1][aljazeera.com#2] (<a href='https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/21-dead-in-gaza-as-israel-hamas-trade-truce-violation-allegations-9683768#publisher=newsstand'>NDTV; Al Jazeera</a>)</li><li>Gaza civil defence/health officials: Local officials report between 21 and 24 people killed and dozens wounded in multiple strikes [al-monitor.com#1][pbs.org#1][bbc.com#1] (<a href='https://www.al-monitor.com/originals/2025/11/gaza-civil-defence-says-21-killed-israeli-strikes-0'>Al-Monitor; PBS; BBC</a>)</li><li>Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu’s office: The government says five senior Hamas members were killed in the strikes [pbs.org#1][france24.com#2] (<a href='https://www.pbs.org/newshour/world/israel-launches-strikes-in-gaza-ceasefires-latest-test-as-hospitals-say-24-people-killed'>PBS; France 24</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/21-dead-in-gaza-as-israel-hamas-trade-truce-violation-allegations-9683768#publisher=newsstand'>21 Dead In Gaza As Israel, Hamas Trade Truce Violation Allegations</a> - ndtv.com</li><li><a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2025/11/22/world/middleeast/israeli-strikes-gaza.html'>20 Killed in Israeli Strikes as Israel and Hamas Trade Blame Over Truce</a> - nytimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/video/newsfeed/2025/11/22/israel-launches-fresh-wave-of-deadly-air-strikes-across-gaza'>Israel lau